


made on windows
python 3.8.10

to install the dependancies :
make install-virtualenv

to enter the virtualenv :
local.vifrtualenv/Scripts/activate

to run the script :
python threat_finder.py

command options are:
 -> -v or --verbose to print the domains name being considered
threats to the console
 -> -n or --no-file to not write the identified threats in a file
 -> -f or --filename to choose the identified threats filename

can be used for a quick debug as follow :
python threat_finder.py -v -n
